# Production deploys (Netlify)

- **Netlify auto-publishes from `main` only** (`circleoflifealf` / `Circle-of-Life`). Pushes to other branches do not update production.
- **When a segment is ready to ship:** merge into `main` (PR or local merge) and `git push origin main` so Netlify builds. Do not rely on long-lived feature branches for production visibility.
- Prefer short-lived branches + PR into `main`, or commit directly on `main` for small gated segments, per team preference.
